[Comparison of open and minimally invasive techniques in the surgical treatment 
of intradural extramedullary spinal tumors in elderly and senile patients.].

[Article in Russian; Abstract available in Russian from the publisher]

Byvaltsev VA(1)(2)(3)(4), Stepanov IA(1), Aliyev MA(1).

Author information:
(1)Irkutsk State Medical University, 1, Krasnogo Vosstaniya str., Irkutsk, 
664003, Russian Federation; e mail: byval75vadim@yandex.ru.
(2)Railway Clinical Hospital on the station of Irkutsk-Passazhirkii, 
Neurosurgical Center, 10, Botkina str., Irkutsk, 664005, Russian Federation.
(3)Irkutsk Scientific Center of Surgery and Traumatology, Bortsov Revolutsii 
