Diagnosis of obesity and use of obesity biomarkers in science and clinical 
medicine.

Nimptsch K(1), Konigorski S(2), Pischon T(3).

Author information:
(1)Molecular Epidemiology Research Group, Max Delbrück Center for Molecular 
Medicine (MDC), Berlin, Germany. Electronic address: 
katharina.nimptsch@mdc-berlin.de.
(2)Molecular Epidemiology Research Group, Max Delbrück Center for Molecular 
