Cost-Effectiveness of Transcatheter Versus Surgical Aortic Valve Replacement in 
Patients With Severe Aortic Stenosis at Intermediate Risk.

Baron SJ(1), Wang K(1), House JA(2), Magnuson EA(1), Reynolds MR(3), Makkar 
R(4), Herrmann HC(5), Kodali S(6), Thourani VH(7), Kapadia S(8), Svensson L(8), 
Mack MJ(9), Brown DL(9), Russo MJ(10), Smith CR(6), Webb J(11), Miller C(12), 
